OL,3,CSunderland confirm appointment of
OL,4,CMichael Beale as Tony Mowbray's
OL,5,Csuccessor
OL,7,FSunderland have confirmed the
OL,8,Fappointment of Michael Beale as their
OL,9,Fnew head coach.
OL,11,FThe Black Cats have been on the
OL,12,Flookout for a new boss since the
OL,13,Fsacking of Tony Mowbray two weeks ago
OL,14,Fwith coach Mike Dodds taking temporary
OL,15,Fcharge.
OL,17,FBeale, who was himself sacked by
OL,18,FRangers two months ago, will now take
OL,19,Fover the reins in the long term after
OL,20,Fsigning a contract until the summer of
OL,21,F2026.
